name: 21 Banshee
description: There’s a peculiar phenomenon that occurs in a southern kingdom. According to the legend, women from this kingdom have mysteriously woken up on ‘The Other Side’. Now this wouldn’t be such a cause for concern had it not for been strange situation they find themselves in, in which they are completely inaudible to the humans of ‘The Other Side’. At one point it became so common the humans on ‘The Other Side’ began referring to these women as Banshee, an omen of death.
